  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2812714">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2812714/" class="title-link">一颗冷酷的心</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2812714"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mado1983/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1088376-22.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mado1983/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">mado1983</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-02"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-02 12:32:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2812714_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这几年，很多专栏作家也都结集出书了，有的还不错，有的就相当一般。  回国工作以后，买书便利了很多，加上工作压力越来越大，排解的方式我选择买书。被老板表扬了高兴，要买书奖励一下自己，事情做得不合老板心意被要求返工感觉郁闷，要买书平复一下心情，一整天电话不断好不...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2812714/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 7没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2812714_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2812714_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
