          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/No1-marine/" class=" " title="萤光糖">萤光糖</a>
                (No.1 Marine,your second harbor)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14095862">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">是不是人长大了,开始思考，就会更偏向于看杂文呢？
嗯，这本杂文有点无厘头，但是还是让我思考挺多。</span>
